gw.api.web.payment

Class DBPaymentDistItemGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.payment.DBPaymentDistItemGroup
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DBPaymentDistItemsForCustomGroup, DBPaymentDistItemsForInvoice, DBPaymentDistItemsForTAccountOwner

    public abstract class DBPaymentDistItemGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    A group of a payment's distribution items for the New Direct Bill Payment Screen. The group is responsible for holding the individual distribution items as well as providing information about the group as a whole, such as the group's display name and the total unbilled amount of the group.
